name: Reindeers in the night
description:
Reindeer are not only for children; they are for grandmothers fond of watching the moon.

This painting was created in Oct'2021 in acrylic colors on ivory paper sheet by fluid painting technique. 
Please connect with me on twitter @singh99abhay or email me- abhay99.tez@gmail.com if you wish to know more about this painting.
